Preeti Pawar (born 23 October 2003) is an Indian boxer. She won a bronze medal in the women's 54 kg event at the 2022 Asian Games.
Early life
She was born on 23 October 2003 in Bhiwani, Haryana. She was inspired by her parents to take up sports as both of her parents are former athletes. After her parents recognised her sports potential, they encouraged her to follow her sports dreams.
